social_posts.post_text:
Thank you for everything, Rick. 

You showed me what it means to be a hard worker and a true competitor. From a young player to now, you are someone that I will always look up to. 

Happy retirement!
Thank you @capt.chrisargiro for putting us onto some great fish! Absolute amazing way to spend the weekend.
No better way to see Arizona

This past weekend was Deaf and hard of hearing night with the Red Sox. I was super honored to take part. 

ASL was my first language growing up. It was taught to me by my mom who is a sign language interpreter. 

Because of that this community always has a special place in my heart 🤟
